        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-02",
        "text": "I wish I could give Bound for the mountains more than 5 stars, they deserve it! My fiancé and I recently traveled to Breckenridge and little did I know, I’d be paired with a photographer on a dog sledding trip and be getting proposed too! My fiancé contacted Andrea and Rachel from Bound to the mountains months ago and planned a surprise engagement while we were dog sledding. Andrea and Rachel were amazing to work with and made this day extremely special to us! Rachel played it off so well and captured everything we could imagine. We just received our photos the other day and they are absolutely breathtaking. My fiancé and I can’t put into words how grateful we are to have worked with such wonderful people. I cannot recommend them enough!!"
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-09",
        "text": "They captured the greatest day of my life. Couldn't have dreamed of or scripted it any better. Working with Andrea and Leah from planning the proposal, scripting \"the story\" to tell my fiance the day of, and shooting photos/videos of our happiness after she said yes...I loved every moment of it."
      },
      {
        "rating": 5,
        "when": "2023-02",
        "text": "There aren’t enough words in colorado to express how incredible our experience with Rachel and Andrea was or how special our photos came out! This is truly a special photography group, and the love, care, and kindness comes through in all their interactions and photos taken. When Mother Nature had other plans for our outdoor shoot in the dead of winter, Rachel and Andrea worked with us and every option possible to make sure we got our shoot in and could not have been more caring or wonderful. Show me another photographer who would take photos in -13 degrees with the biggest smile! We are so incredibly thankful to Rachel, Andrea, and the entire Bound team. Thank you for creating these memories with us!"
      },
